creditors, many of whom
are angry they will
have to eat big losses

05:47.166 --> 05:49.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
in bankruptcy court.

05:49.166 --> 05:52.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Thousands of protesters took
to the streets this week as
the pain spreads throughout the

05:52.333 --> 05:54.400 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
island.

05:54.400 --> 05:58.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
