conversation with different
creditors, and our hope
is that we can find

06:36.666 --> 06:41.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
a consensual renegotiation
route based on the fiscal plan
that we have implemented and

06:43.433 --> 06:45.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
that's been certified
for Puerto Rico.

06:45.000 --> 06:48.000 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Well, how
much worse is it going to get?

06:48.000 --> 06:51.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
