06:53.533 --> 06:55.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
What other public services
are you going to have
to tighten your belt on?

06:55.533 --> 06:57.533 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
GOV.

06:57.533 --> 07:00.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
RICARDO ROSSELLO: Well, the
schools initiative was one that
was established for a couple

07:00.900 --> 07:03.000 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of months.

07:03.000 --> 07:05.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We have just announced today
which schools are the ones
that were going to be closed

07:05.133 --> 07:07.166 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
now.

07:07.166 --> 07:11.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This initiative, of course,
has some fiscal relief, but the
objective is for our children

07:11.066 --> 07:16.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
to actually consolidate
and that we can get
more human resource to
give a better service

07:17.200 --> 07:18.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
to the kids, to the
children of Puerto Rico.

