receive higher will start
getting a progressive
cut on their pension.

08:10.100 --> 08:12.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Governor,
I know Puerto Rico is home to
you and it's home to the people

08:12.033 --> 08:14.100 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
