08:31.800 --> 08:33.833 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
GOV.

08:33.833 --> 08:36.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
RICARDO ROSSELLO: That's been
happening so far because we
haven't made the proper changes.

08:36.900 --> 08:39.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
