Puerto Rico, for jobs to be
created, and for opportunities

09:04.900 --> 09:06.866 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to ensue.

09:06.866 --> 09:10.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And our objective, again, is
for Puerto Rico, for the people
of Puerto Rico who want to

09:12.333 --> 09:14.766 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
stay here, for them to have
the opportunity to stay here.

09:14.766 --> 09:17.866 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Now, there's one last
thing we need to point out.

09:17.866 --> 09:22.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And it is a fact that Puerto
Rico is a colonial territory
of the United States.

09:22.166 --> 09:27.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
