significant disadvantage
to all of the other
states and to all of the

09:27.066 --> 09:29.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
other American citizens.

09:29.166 --> 09:33.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
As a matter of comparative,
the U.S. citizens, the Puerto
Ricans that live in the United

09:35.400 --> 09:39.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
States have much better incomes,
more than twice as much,
participate in the labor force

09:41.700 --> 09:45.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
