better results in the
education system and so forth.

09:47.400 --> 09:52.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And the one key difference
is that Puerto Rico is
a colonial territory.

09:53.100 --> 09:54.766 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
