getting funding from
the federal government.

09:57.900 --> 10:02.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
So, this is another
critical component
that we need to change.

10:02.233 --> 10:06.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: So,
in the meantime, as your
population continues to
move to the mainland,

10:06.733 --> 10:09.966 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
your tax base shrinks, which
only compounds this problem.

10:09.966 --> 10:10.966 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
GOV.

10:10.966 --> 10:11.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
RICARDO ROSSELLO: Right.

10:11.966 --> 10:13.500 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
