20:26.000 --> 20:29.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
BRIAN ADEBA, The Enough
Project: Well, indeed
what he said is true.

20:29.733 --> 20:34.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
At independence, a small
group of people in the ruling
party, a small group of elites

20:34.400 --> 20:39.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
