within the party.

20:43.800 --> 20:48.800 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Ultimately, in the end,
rivalries started appearing
in the party because
of this corruption.

20:52.933 --> 20:57.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The state became the most
prized asset that everyone
was vying for control of.

20:57.800 --> 21:02.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Unfortunately, for the ruling
party itself, because it had
incapacitated the ability of

21:04.800 --> 21:09.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
institutions to mitigate this
conflict, in the end, the
conflict began to be expressed

21:10.933 --> 21:12.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
in violent terms.

21:12.166 --> 21:14.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And that's where
we are right now.

21:14.200 --> 21:15.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: So,
stopping the conflict is the
first priority for everyone.

21:15.800 --> 21:17.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Why hasn't worked?

21:17.533 --> 21:20.233 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Why hasn't it worked so
far, whatever we have tried?

21:20.233 --> 21:24.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NII AKUETTEH: I think one
of the methods, one of the
measures that people have talked

21:24.366 --> 21:29.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
about that have not actually
implemented is stopping the
flow of arms into the country.

21:30.566 --> 21:33.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
It's like pouring
gasoline on fire.

21:33.033 --> 21:37.500 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And various international
players behind the
scenes are reluctant,
both in the region and

21:39.233 --> 21:40.433 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
then globally.

21:40.433 --> 21:41.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I think that's
one of the things.

21:41.933 --> 21:44.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But the other thing is
that not enough pressure.

21:44.033 --> 21:48.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I mean, the people who are doing
