fighting, they have not suffered

21:50.466 --> 21:52.566 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
from it.

21:52.566 --> 21:56.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I think one other aspect of
the fighting that needs to be
stressed is, heartbreakingly,

21:58.400 --> 22:01.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
