so that ordinary people
are being killed.

22:01.233 --> 22:02.966 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
There are ethnic militias.

22:02.966 --> 22:07.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
So I think stopping it
will be -- is going to
be quite a challenge.

22:07.066 --> 22:09.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
BRIAN ADEBA: It's true.

22:09.133 --> 22:13.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The missing element here is
leverage, what can be done to
exert leverage, so that the

22:15.400 --> 22:17.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
parties in the conflict
change their calculations
towards peace.

22:17.900 --> 22:19.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
That's been missing.

22:19.866 --> 22:23.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we have suggested that
targeted pressures, targeted
sanctions are essential, an arms

22:24.766 --> 22:27.333 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
embargo.

22:27.333 --> 22:30.766 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Targeted sanctions are
essential because most of
these transactions happen
in the U.S. dollars.

22:32.766 --> 22:36.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And that gives the U.S.
jurisdiction to act
within the toolkit here,
the precious toolkit

22:37.466 --> 22:39.733 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
available to
policy-makers in the U.S.

22:39.733 --> 22:44.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
There are measures that can
be enacted to trace these
assets, to seize these assets

22:46.733 --> 22:49.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
in some aspects, and to send
a message to the perpetrators
of this conflict that there

22:49.833 --> 22:51.966 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
is a price to pay for war.

22:51.966 --> 22:54.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Is that the
most effective way to do it,
because the U.S. dollar is the

22:54.800 --> 22:56.933 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
