opportunity to use that.

24:56.766 --> 24:58.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Is that the
best way for us to move forward?

24:58.833 --> 25:01.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Is it through a body
like the United Nations?

25:01.366 --> 25:03.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Is there something the
