be doing independent?

25:03.933 --> 25:06.733 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
NII AKUETTEH: I think so.

25:06.733 --> 25:11.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The region original organization
IGAD, Sudan, Uganda, Kenya,
Ethiopia, all of them have

25:15.400 --> 25:17.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
played a great role.

25:17.033 --> 25:21.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
And, in fact, up until
some time ago, they
played a positive role.

25:21.100 --> 25:25.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But now, in fact, the reason
that there has been no push on
the leadership in South Sudan

25:25.433 --> 25:28.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
